              I am a systems engineering and computer science student at the
              Technological University of Peru. I am a lover of code and
              technology, every day I learn something new about programming or
              new technologies
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/6 flex justify-end">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-b from-luis-blue-dark/0 to-luis-blue-dark mr-8 h-full w-1 md:mr-16 lg:mr-0"
