    <div id="projects" class="bg-luis-blue-lighter">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
        <div class="project">
          <div class="project-container-line">
            <div class="project-line bg-luis-blue-dark">
              <div class="project-date">01/23</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-container">
            <div class="project-card">
              <img
                src="./img/projects/twitch-kill-me.jpg"
                alt="a.png"
                class="project-img"
              />
              <div class="project-title">Twitch Kill Me</div>
              <div class="project-text">
                TwitchKillMe is a plugin built for Minecraft and introduces
                Twitch Streamers for Minecraft vs Chat events, it's easy and
                simplified for new users.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
          <div class="project-container-line">
            <div class="project-line bg-luis-blue-dark">
              <div class="project-date">09/22</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-container">
            <div class="project-card">
              <img
                src="./img/projects/uni-developed-software.png"
                alt="a.png"
                class="project-img"
              />
              <div class="project-title">Uni developed software</div>
              <div class="project-text">
                This is my favorite repository, where I upload my projects
                developed for the university. There are already discord bots,
                arduino projects and javascript projects. I expect much
              </div>
