            <div class="project-card">
              <img
                src="./img/projects/random-tp.png"
                alt="a.png"
                class="project-img"
              />
              <div class="project-title">Random TP</div>
              <div class="project-text">
                RandomTP is a plugin created in order to simplify and improve
                the alternatives that already exist. This is a simple project
                and I'll try to keep it up to date regarding minecraft versions
                etc.
              </div>
